  "title": "chore(website): prepare for v3",
  "body": "This makes the community website ready to host the InstantSearch.js 3 documentation:\r\n\r\n- Move \"/dev-novel\" to \"/stories\" (like [Vue InstantSearch](https://v2--vue-instantsearch.netlify.com/stories))\r\n- Move \"/v2\" links to root\r\n- Change from \"v1\" link to \"v2\"\r\n- Remove Docsearch searchbox (because it redirects to v2)\r\n- Rename \"dev\" folder to \"storybook\" to gradually migrate to Storybook\r\n\r\n## Previews\r\n\r\n- Website: https://deploy-preview-3265--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/\r\n- Stories: https://deploy-preview-3265--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/stories",
